501
00:29:56,130 --> 00:29:58,370
Apa itu saja?

502
00:29:58,400 --> 00:29:59,600
Ya.

503
00:29:59,630 --> 00:30:01,340
Aku butuh sesuatu kepunyaan Boyd
untuk ditanam...

504
00:30:01,370 --> 00:30:04,270
