505
00:30:07,510 --> 00:30:08,940
Dompetnya.

506
00:30:08,980 --> 00:30:10,980
Bagaimana kau tahu ada disitu?

507
00:30:11,010 --> 00:30:13,250
Aku yang menaruhnya.

508
00:30:13,280 --> 00:30:16,450
Dengar semuanya!

509
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:18,320
