515
00:30:31,770 --> 00:30:33,670
Itu dia, bukan milik Cole.

516
00:30:33,700 --> 00:30:35,570
Lalu milik siapa?

517
00:30:35,600 --> 00:30:39,010
Boyd Fowler.

518
00:30:39,040 --> 00:30:42,640
Siapa itu Boyd Fowler?

519
00:30:44,110 --> 00:30:49,780
Aku akan ke lantai atas.

520
00:30:49,820 --> 00:30:51,850
Lihat ini.

521
00:30:51,890 --> 00:30:54,450
