558
00:32:29,450 --> 00:32:33,150
Dia berbahaya.

559
00:32:33,190 --> 00:32:38,060
Dia datang dan pergi
ke kantor kami beberapa kali.

560
00:32:38,090 --> 00:32:40,160
Mungkin dia lihat
dimana aku meletakkan kunci.

561
00:32:40,190 --> 00:32:42,400
Kapan terakhir kau bertemu dengannya?

562
00:32:42,430 --> 00:32:45,970
Sudah lama tak melihat dia.

563
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:47,400
Mungkin sudah dua bulan.

564
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:49,270
Kira-kira kau tahu dimana dia berada?

565
00:32:49,300 --> 00:32:52,740
Tidak.

566
00:32:52,770 --> 00:32:56,410
Kami punya surat penangkapannya.

567
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:59,910
Saya menyarankan
Anda berhati-hati, Tn. Chase,...

568
00:32:59,950 --> 00:33:01,580
