569
00:33:01,620 --> 00:33:03,050
...Anda bisa dalam bahaya.

570
00:33:03,080 --> 00:33:05,190
Saya mengerti.

571
00:33:05,220 --> 00:33:06,690
Jika Anda bertemu dengan dia,..

572
00:33:06,720 --> 00:33:08,920
