00:36:43,440 --> 00:36:48,380
Baiklah.

642
00:36:54,120 --> 00:36:56,350
Kau tak perlu melakukan apapun, oke?

643
00:36:56,380 --> 00:36:58,020
Kau bisa bicara normal.

644
00:36:58,050 --> 00:36:59,520
Apa yang harus kulakukan?

645
00:36:59,550 --> 00:37:00,990
Kami akan mengantarmu sampai klub...

646
00:37:01,020 --> 00:37:02,490
