00:38:34,720 --> 00:38:37,480
Lalu saat mereka keluar kita tangkap.

674
00:38:37,520 --> 00:38:39,190
Pastikan kita menemukan pintu rahasia...

675
00:38:39,220 --> 00:38:40,420
